data.description: Step into your new home and immediately experience the open concept living area featuring 2 bedrooms and a spacious master bedroom with a loft that provides an extra touch to your private sanctuary. Convenience is paramount with 3 full bathrooms, one on each level. Discover a fully finished basement with a wood-burning stove and a walk-out to the backyard. Relax on the recently painted large front porch or back deck overlooking the large back yard. This home strikes the perfect balance, situated conveniently close to shopping centers and the highway while maintaining the tranquil feel.
